entry.title: slowlydev/f1-dash
entry.summary:
A real-time F1 dashboard

Real-time Formula 1 telemetry and timing

f1-dash

A real-time F1 dashboard that shows the leader board, tires, gaps, laps, mini sectors and much more

contributing

I really appreciate it if you want to contribute to this project. I can recommend the GitHub issues marked as "Good First Issue" to get started. Also please read CONTRIBUTING.md to learn how to contribute and setup f1-dash on your local machine for development.

supporting

If you want to support me and make me focus more on this project, support me here by buying me a coffee.
